      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like i'm already gone, you know? like i'm just performing some role for Estas/Slack/Zoom every day just to keep a space occupied. the thought of just... not doing it anymore... not having to pretend... it feels more like a relief than anything scary. it's like a silence that i actually want.",
